videos.description: Grayson Allen is trapped with the shot clock winding down, and he heaves up a 3-pointer for the buzzer-beater bucket.
videos.headline: Duke's Allen makes spectacular shot

videos.description: Grayson Allen scores a driving floater then on the ensuing possession makes a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Allen's getting buckets for Duke

videos.description: Grayson Allen passes to Wendell Carter who finds Javin DeLaurier for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: The ball never touches the floor on Blue Devils' dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen scores 25 points and goes 7-of-15 from deep to lead Duke to a 74-52 win over Virginia Tech.
videos.headline: Allen hot from downtown in Duke's win
